item.title: Greet The Gaffer with Chris Agutter
item.description:
What gives a new manager confidence even when his team is struggling? Find out as the new Sutton United Gaffer, Chris Agutter, joins us for a very special Greet The Gaffer episode of Sutton United Talk Time on Podcast!


Host Mike Dowling sits down with Chris Agutter to discuss his first few intense weeks at Gander Green Lane, his deep-seated football philosophy influenced by 'Votel football' and Johan Cruyff, and the critical role of authentic, empathetic leadership in the modern...
